Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.97,0:00:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在回想起來，自從那天以來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.14,0:00:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來過這裏多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.58,0:00:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個國度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，在這個星球\N我思念的只有一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那小小的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.25,0:00:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.25,0:00:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏是我和千瀨的定情之處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.17,0:01:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在那天，從這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.54,0:01:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這個地方開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（阿修）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.01,0:02:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動作會不會太慢了啊，千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是慢吞吞的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,個子又小，膽子也很小
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且又笨手笨腳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成績也只有中下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有世界史好得莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這無法成為\N將來謀生的一技之長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她自己也很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的口頭禪是「對不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的座右銘是\N「想要變得更堅強」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼看都覺得是個\N沒有用的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.15,0:03:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天還是像以前一樣\N搭公交車上學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想跟我一起爬地獄坡\N是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟我不久以前還是田徑隊的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是，我還是得跟你一起上學才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為，我是你的女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交換日記？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然不喜歡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰慫恿你做這種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是明美他們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我真的想多瞭解你一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，你們兩個\N不快點就會遲到喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明美，早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又在欺負千瀨嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒有欺負她！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，要遲到了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法，我就陪你寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的女朋友，千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五天前她向我表白\N要我跟她交往
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在依然猶豫不決
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交換日記啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦，你就陪她寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正晚上\N也沒有什麼事情可以做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電視老是在回放\N不然就是放電影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說手機跟網絡\N現在又不能用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我該寫什麼好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛，比如說\N你今天一整天做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是去了什麼地方之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正到了暑假\N就不會一直在一起了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.43,0:05:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了學校和家裏之外\N我還有什麼地方能去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然你就寫\N你喜歡千瀨什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是想跟她接吻\N想跟她嘿咻之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說這個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹，你跟由佳利上床了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯，畢竟我們交往兩個月了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然已經上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說來聽嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不說\N因為說了會被你們當笑柄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點點就好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，等等我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去撿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨，修次在看你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，明美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向她揮揮手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然又會被明美臭罵喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,F-15
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近經常在飛耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會是發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說東京和大阪那邊挺危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會有事的啦，反正跟我們無關
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交換日記啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，你現在在做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在當然是在看日記啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.92,0:07:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得我提起勇氣向你告白\N真的是做對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在每天都過得好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想…千瀨，你好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假就快要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什麼計劃…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在搞什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，你在睡覺嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我醒著啦，現在就去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟女生交往，原來這麼麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，我們要先吃囉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要一直叫我阿修啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏可以隨便進去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:09:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會被罵嗎？這是基地裏面耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係，反正只是基地的邊緣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.49,0:09:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前都可以自由進出的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他終於把交換日記還你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了，千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（還是算了吧不過放學後陪我一下）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不出所料\N我可以瞭解修次的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放學後…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是指「嘿咻」嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，我們沒迷路吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏半個人都沒有耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得現在還太早…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後我想讓你看看這個景色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉，我已經累了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這個人不適合談戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起，並不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.77,0:11:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也覺得很累啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道男女交往\N該做些什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.51,0:11:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拚命的問明美\N還看了一堆漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試著去做好多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全無法像別人一樣\N順利的談戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歸根究底都是你的錯啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我根本就沒想要跟你交往！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是為了試試膽量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改變我軟弱的個性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為明美知道我一直很崇拜你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.05,0:11:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就叫我向你表白\N想說失敗也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道你竟然答應跟我交往
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般都會答應吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要答應我？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你這麼可愛的女孩告白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家當然會答應啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你向人家告白前\N人家根本沒打算和女生交往
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.95,0:12:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.01,0:12:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「人家」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.39,0:12:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從小時候就這樣說話\N這有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起，你好可愛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜！你比較可愛啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實，我真的很怕你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要一直說對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交往至今\N我好像是第一次看到你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.75,0:13:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許男女交往就像這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還是男朋友和女朋友吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然順序有點混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得有緣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後我們要不要\N試著去喜歡對方看看？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.49,0:14:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.73,0:14:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼，你希望我對你做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了，我做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們打算從這裏\N開始我們的戀情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:15:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心臟跳得好大聲喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個鄉下的小鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.52,0:15:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然沒有任何樂趣可言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對未來也是茫茫然的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我們兩人\N已經決定了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要繼續相戀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以偶爾打電話給你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊\N路上小心點，不要跌倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起，咖啡賣完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由佳利和阿竹在吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.54,0:16:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜，不要隨便認定\N他們是在吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，我向你道歉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個傷怎麼來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又在家裏跌倒了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.79,0:16:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼，不要緊的，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的很粗心大意耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微小心一點喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟你是個女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，我們兩個也會吵架嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該吵不起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你經常哼這首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜歡這首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.99,0:17:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.77,0:17:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我們要代替那個\N最後突然說不來的千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪你來札幌大採購呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少廢話，閉上你的嘴巴快選啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒女朋友還要來買服飾\N只是更空虛而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要請我吃烤玉米喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豬頭，你是觀光客啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是玫瑰水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是愛與療傷的寶石
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好喔，我也要買給我女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們兩個吵架還沒和好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是地震
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，這個地震很強喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像越來越近了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，去外面看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要出去，阿淳\N這時候亂跑很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.95,0:18:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊，避難訓練時學過了不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豬頭，別在這裏說風涼話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.53,0:18:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是哪裏的戰鬥機？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我們國家的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:18:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底出了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之往大道公園逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊，這裏太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿淳，你看上面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是F-2，從三澤來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.47,0:19:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往這裏來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.37,0:19:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次，快點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個鐘樓才剛剛修好的說．
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿律，快逃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，修次，阿律，阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.06,0:19:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼？到底是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹，喂，阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹，你不可以死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快來救救他，來人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身體變成了這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.52,0:21:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在回想起來\N那時候我應該察覺到才對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.51,0:22:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.91,0:22:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我抱著千瀨\N她的心臟卻沒有心跳聲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.15,0:22:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,#01 我們將繼續相戀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.60,0:22:43.51,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心中有一道裂縫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:50.45,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,難以入眠的夜裏總不停的嘆息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:23:00.15,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不覺黎明已悄然到來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.23,0:23:09.06,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,多麼想聽見你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.13,0:23:13.16,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,感受你的體溫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.24,0:23:20.47,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,對你的思念越來越強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:25.21,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,淚水奪眶而出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.28,0:23:30.35,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了我心愛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.42,0:23:36.55,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,我仍無法忘懷你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.63,0:23:41.46,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然只因一句再見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.53,0:23:46.97,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,就要結束一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.04,0:23:52.10,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,叫人感到悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨，你說你變成終極武器\N是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.35,0:24:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要上戰場打仗一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.16,0:24:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還只是高中生耶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.12,0:24:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.39,0:24:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最終兵器彼女下一回\N「我正在成長」

